      <h3>The 6 Phases of SDLC</h3>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-num">1</div><div class="step-content"><strong>Planning:</strong> Define the problem. Feasibility study (technical, economic, operational). Determine if the project is worth doing. Output: Feasibility Report.</div></div>
